txt.en: 'Does it bother you that your lives will end here?'
Doom-speaker extinquishes a Rune, summoning forth Darklings.
'You have gone too far!  This earth is mine!  Now, you are mine!'
Gurvand screams mightily, the echoes shaking the walls.  The shadows seem to creep in even closer.
A vile gust of wind sweeps through the passages, shaking the very walls of the cave.  Only the glowing rocks seem unaffected.
Once Void-eater is killed, you can use this chest.
Once Doom-speaker is killed, you can use this chest.
Once Gurvand is killed, you can use this chest.
As the bright light shines, an ancient chest crumbles into dust.
'And then there were these few who stood before me, destined to go no further.'
Doom-speaker extinquishes a Rune, summoning forth Headless.
'Who dares come here?  I smell flesh.  Food for my sweets.'
Doom-speaker extinquishes a Rune, summoning forth Faceless.
Doom-speaker extinquishes a Rune, summoning forth a World-eater.
